        <briefdescription>
<para>Read current pin state and emit EVT unconditionally — no debounce. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Called by <ref refid="namespacePanelGroup" kindref="compound">PanelGroup</ref> during the boot EVT burst and on SYNC_REQ. Confirms the current reading as the baseline so subsequent <ref refid="classOpenSkyhawk_1_1Switch2Pos_1a678c017bf049459445851b5d3e9cf84f" kindref="member">poll()</ref> calls have a valid reference. </para>
